          <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)]">
            <strong>“Customer Content”</strong> means content you (or your users) upload, submit, or transmit to the
            Service, including prompts, messages, documents, files, configuration data, and outputs you choose to store.
          </p>
