            <li><strong>You are responsible</strong> for Customer Content, the agents you configure, and how you use outputs.</li>
            <li><strong>AI output is not guaranteed.</strong> Outputs may be inaccurate, incomplete, offensive, or unsafe. You are responsible for evaluating outputs before using or relying on them.</li>
          </ul>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-4 mb-2">License to operate the Service</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)]">
            You grant us a worldwide, non-exclusive license to host, store, reproduce, process, transmit, and display
            Customer Content <strong>only as needed</strong> to provide, secure, and improve the Service, comply with
            law, and enforce these Terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="rounded-xl p-6 mb-6 border border-neon-cyan/20 bg-surface-100/80 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-4">7. Third-party services and integrations</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)]">
            The Service may integrate with third-party services (for example: AI model providers, messaging platforms,
            analytics, secure sign-in (OAuth) providers, and other APIs). Your use of third-party services is governed by their terms and
            privacy policies.
