          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="rounded-xl p-6 mb-6 border border-neon-cyan/20 bg-surface-100/80 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-4">8. Billing, plans, credits, and provider charges</h2>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-2">Platform subscription vs AI provider charges</h3>
          <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)]">
            Your Helpmaton subscription fees cover platform functionality (such as workspaces, agent configuration,
            dashboards, document search, and Helpmaton API access). AI model usage may involve <strong>separate costs</strong>.
