          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-1 ml-4 text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)] mb-4">
            <li><strong>Bring Your Own Key (BYOK):</strong> You may add your own provider key (for example via OpenRouter). In that case, <strong>you pay the provider directly</strong> under the provider’s terms, and charges are between you and the provider.</li>
