            WE DO NOT WARRANT THAT THE SERVICE WILL BE UNINTERRUPTED, ERROR-FREE, OR SECURE, OR THAT OUTPUTS WILL BE
            ACCURATE OR RELIABLE.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="rounded-xl p-6 mb-6 border border-neon-cyan/20 bg-surface-100/80 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-4">12. Limitation of liability</h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)]">TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW:</p>
